            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Update Mac CodexBar to **0.23.4 (Build 58.4.1.3.1) or later** for the new providers and accurate Cost numbers — earlier 0.23.x has a Codex parser bug. Download: [github.com/o1xhack/CodexBar-Mobile/releases](https://github.com/o1xhack/CodexBar-Mobile/releases)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
