    "Version 1.2.0 works best with the latest CodexBar Mac app (0.19.0 or later). Utilization History sync relies on Mac-side fixes shipped in that release. Download from GitHub: github.com/o1xhack/CodexBar-Mobile/releases": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Version 1.2.0 works best with the latest CodexBar Mac app (0.19.0 or later). Utilization History sync relies on Mac-side fixes shipped in that release. Download from GitHub: github.com/o1xhack/CodexBar-Mobile/releases"
